22:02.755 --> 22:04.018
- HOWARD: Come on, now...
- Will you people quiet down?

22:04.156 --> 22:05.487
You're giving me a headache.

22:05.624 --> 22:07.251
Quiet, Richard,
and don't interrupt your father.

22:07.393 --> 22:08.622
Thank you, Marion.

22:08.761 --> 22:10.524
Now, look, Fon...

22:10.663 --> 22:11.687
Richard!

22:11.830 --> 22:12.889
- Oh, Richard!
- Richard?

22:13.032 --> 22:14.693
- You're okay!
- Are you all right?

22:14.833 --> 22:16.165
- Are you all right, dear?
- Doctor! Doctor!

22:16.302 --> 22:17.496
FONZIE:
Oh, man, it is good to see you.

22:17.636 --> 22:18.831
- Hey! -Oh, you gave us
a terrible scare.

22:18.971 --> 22:20.996
I-ls... is Lori Beth all right?

22:21.140 --> 22:22.130
- Oh, she's fine, just fine.
- Yes.

22:22.274 --> 22:23.537
Oh, good.

22:23.676 --> 22:25.837
Hey.

22:25.978 --> 22:26.843
How do you feel?

22:26.979 --> 22:29.414
Well, uh...

22:29.548 --> 22:31.073
I feel kind of hungry.

22:31.217 --> 22:32.081
Oh...

22:32.218 --> 22:33.583
- That's a good sign.
- Yeah.

22:33.719 --> 22:35.312
Oh, Richard.

22:35.454 --> 22:37.445
Oh, I'm so glad
to see your eyes open...

22:40.426 --> 22:42.417
Heyyy.

23:04.650 --> 23:05.913
All right. All right.

23:06.051 --> 23:07.383
Where there's a will,
there's a way.

23:07.519 --> 23:09.078
All right, try this.

23:09.221 --> 23:10.780
Hmm? Huh?

23:10.923 --> 23:12.914
- Yeah. (laughs)
- Ah.

23:17.263 --> 23:20.664
I told you he'd be
his old self before long.

23:20.799 --> 23:22.426
(clears throat loudly)

23:22.568 --> 23:23.660
- Oh, hello, Mr...
-(yells)

23:23.802 --> 23:26.704
"Oh!
