23:30.676 --> 23:32.906
Richard,
your motorcycle's fixed.

23:33.045 --> 23:34.342
No, no, I'm not keeping that.

23:34.480 --> 23:35.970
I'm-I'm getting rid
of that motorcycle.

23:36.115 --> 23:37.048
Good.

23:37.182 --> 23:38.047
Yeah, you know, I wanted

23:38.183 --> 23:39.116
one of those for so long,

23:39.251 --> 23:40.184
and then when I got it,

23:40.319 --> 23:42.481
I was scared to death
to ride it.

23:42.621 --> 23:44.055
I don't know,
I-l just don't think

23:44.189 --> 23:45.987
I'm suited for a motorcycle.

23:46.125 --> 23:48.491
Well, it wouldn't
have been much fun

23:48.627 --> 23:49.822
